    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "INTRODUCTION OF THE EDISON ELECTRIC LIGHT",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "The way of the inventor is hard.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "It was not a fact at any time that the public was opposed to the idea of the electric light.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "There also the most bitter feeling was shown.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "In two distinct directions the gas art was immediately helped by Edison's work.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000007_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000007_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "In the second place, the coming of the incandescent light raised the standard of illumination in such a manner that more gas than ever was wanted in order to satisfy the popular demand for brightness and brilliancy both indoors and on the street.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "So much for the early opposition, of which there was plenty.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000011_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000011_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "We moved the lamp works from Menlo Park to Harrison.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000011_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000011_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "We sold them for forty cents; but there were only about twenty or thirty thousand of them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000011_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000011_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "I still sold them for forty cents, and lost more money that year than any other, because the sales were increasing rapidly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "He was discharged, whereupon the union notified us that unless the boy was taken back the whole body would go out.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000012_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000012_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "They were not only more surly; they were diminishing the output, and it became impossible to manage the works.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000012_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000012_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "After feeling around for some days I got a clew how to do it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "For making the dynamos Edison secured, as noted in the preceding chapter, the Roach Iron Works on Goerck Street, New York, and this was also equipped.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000016_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000016_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "This was one of the finest homes in the city of that period, and its acquisition was a premonitory sign of the surrender of the famous residential avenue to commerce.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000016_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000016_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "Finally I opened the pedestal-a storehouse for tools, etc",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "The routine was very much the same as that at the laboratory, in its utter neglect of the clock.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000017_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000017_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "The first year, eighteen eighty one, was naturally that which witnessed the greatest rush of visitors; and the building hardly ever closed its doors till midnight.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000019_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000019_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "Even if I locked them up in my desk they would break it open.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000019_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000019_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "I thought no more about the matter.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000019_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000019_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "I was too busy on other things to notice.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000021_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000021_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "After that, every time he came to New York he used to call at 'sixty five' late at night with his violin.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000021_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000021_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "I would talk for the benefit of his music.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000021_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000021_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "He was good company.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000021_000018",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000021_000018.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "Speaking of telling stories, I once got telling a man stories at the Harrison lamp factory, in the yard, as he was leaving.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000021_000020",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000021_000020.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "I had nothing on to protect me against the cold.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "I did whatever he told me, and looked after all kinds of affairs, from buying his clothes to financing his business.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000025_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000025_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "Edison marginalized documents extensively.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000026_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000026_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "I remember as a coincidence that the building was only twenty feet wide.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000028_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000028_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "As a matter of fact such work began in advance of almost every other kind.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000029_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000029_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "I had caused a printer's composing case to be set up with the idea that if we could get editors and publishers in to see it, we should show them the advantages of the electric light.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000030_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000030_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "This was one of the big 'box houses' on upper Fifth Avenue.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000030_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000030_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "Twombly closed the contract with us for a plant.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000030_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000030_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "mr Herter was doing the decoration, and it was extraordinarily fine.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000030_000019",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000030_000019.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "The houses afterward went onto the New York Edison system.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000033_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000033_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "The important question had arisen, therefore, of satisfying the fire underwriters as to the safety of the system.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1585_131718_000033_000016",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1585/131718/1585_131718_000033_000016.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1585",
        "content": "The process is heroic but costly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
